    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It was just another erotic encounter for Max, one of the most famous porn stars of the 1980s, but things get extra hard when the job requires more limbs than usual after Max and the crew are captured by THE LACERATOR!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339330/extras/d73c4f9a59f177b4883a2a64b04ab8c6.poster.avif?t=1772040211\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339330/extras/d73c4f9a59f177b4883a2a64b04ab8c6.webm?t=1772040211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339330/extras/d73c4f9a59f177b4883a2a64b04ab8c6.mp4?t=1772040211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wriggling to survive, Max will need to risk life and limb to escape the hideout of this crazed psychopath.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339330/extras/9e7452bcd699f8e97ea97f7ff76668a3.poster.avif?t=1772040211\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339330/extras/9e7452bcd699f8e97ea97f7ff76668a3.webm?t=1772040211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339330/extras/9e7452bcd699f8e97ea97f7ff76668a3.mp4?t=1772040211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > GOT LACERATED? Adapt and survive - losing your limbs will change how you play! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore the winding lair of THE LACERATOR</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find items to solve puzzles and progress</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Defend yourself with both melee and ranged weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Manage scavenged resources </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Beware of the many traps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple main paths of play and endings!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game can be played in both fixed camera or over-the-shoulder third person</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339330/extras/567f1eb59e8f63d2a2cd1d9955284624.poster.avif?t=1772040211\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339330/extras/567f1eb59e8f63d2a2cd1d9955284624.webm?t=1772040211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339330/extras/567f1eb59e8f63d2a2cd1d9955284624.mp4?t=1772040211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
